title: HaTemani
typeOfFood: Take-out, Middle Eastern, Yemenite, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small Yemenite restaurant in South Tel Aviv with a mostly blue-collar clientele. Offers a vegetarian plate that is vegan suitable. Ask for the tzalachat tzimchonit. You pick 5 different items, like humus, salads, and falafel.
